query: SELECT * WHERE {?residence dbpedia-owl:abstract ?abstract_en. FILTER (lang(?abstract_en) = 'en') ?residence rdfs:label ?label_en. FILTER (lang(?label_en) = 'en') OPTIONAL {?residence dbpedia-owl:abstract ?abstract_zh. FILTER (lang(?abstract_zh) = 'zh')} OPTIONAL {?residence rdfs:label ?label_zh. FILTER (lang(?label_zh) = 'zh')} OPTIONAL {?residence geo:lat ?latitude. ?residence geo:long ?longtitue.} OPTIONAL {?residence dbpedia-owl:elevation ?elevation} OPTIONAL {?residence dbpedia-owl:utcOffset ?timezone} OPTIONAL {?residence dbpedia-owl:areaTotal ?area} OPTIONAL {?residence dbpedia-owl:populationTotal ?population} OPTIONAL {?residence foaf:homepage ?homepage.} OPTIONAL {?residence foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?wikipage.} }
